Blender cheat sheet:

a - unselect all

Alt + Right mouse - Rotate view

z - change viewport

b - box select

g - transforming (перемещение)
gy - перемещение по y

rx - Rotate by X

s - scale object
sx - scale object by X

Alt -r - revert rotation

Alt-s - revert scale

alt -g - back to normal position

x - delete

shift - a - add an primitive object

h - hide a mesh(object)
alt -h - unhide

m - move to other layer

tab - edit mesh object (можно выбрать определенную точку)

ctrl -tab - select mesh selection mode

shift - B + LMB - zoom on specific area

Ctrl - r split . Scroll up to split on multiple parts. CREATE Edge-loop
g - slide edge loop

shift -d - duplicate object

x - delete face

f - fill ( in edit mode select edges or vertices and press f - it will create face )

shift -f fly camera

F3 - save render result
